        "content": "<p>myunbin opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12743\">PR #12743</a> from <code>myunbin:arithmetic-add-030926</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This PR adds several arithmetic/bitwise simplification rules to Cranelift:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>(x + y) + (-y) ==&gt; x</code></li>\n<li><code>(x | y) - (x &amp; y)  ==&gt;  (x ^ y)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x + y) - (x &amp; y)  ==&gt;  (x | y)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x | y) - (x ^ y)  ==&gt;  (x &amp; y)</code></li>\n<li><code>(~x) + x ==&gt; -1</code></li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>",
